---
title: Pepper Sirloin Steak & Agrodolce Eggplant for Dinner with Orange Sponge Cake & Passionfruit Sauce for Dessert
description: Treat mum to a meal as special as she is! Juicy sirloin steak gets a pepper coating, and pairs perfectly with crispy Parmesan potatoes and tangy agrodolce-topped eggplant. And to satisfy your sweet tooth, a light and fluffy orange sponge cake drizzled with a luscious lemon passionfruit sauce for the perfect balance of zest and sweetness.

